text: Jessica Smith may refer to: *Jessica Smith (editor) (1895–1983), American activist and editor *Jessica Smith (speed skater) (born 1983), Olympic short track speed skater from the United States *Jessica Smith (athlete) (born 1989), Canadian track and field athlete *Jessica Smith (swimmer), Australian Paralympic swimmer *Jessica Smith (actress), portrayed the "Sun Baby" in Teletubbies *Jessica Grace Smith (born 1988), New Zealand actress ==See also== *Jessie Smith (disambiguation) *Jesse Smith (disambiguation)
